          "type": "paragraphs",
          "text": [
            "<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">Welcome to Restaurants from Home with Samsung KX</em>. Samsung KX, the Hub of Innovation, has partnered with a line-up of King’s Cross’ most loved restaurants to inspire you to get creative in the kitchen. Each cookalong will include a step-by-step demonstration, led by one of the restaurant’s top chefs, teaching how to create their most iconic dishes from the comfort of home.",
            "This Valentine’s Day, we’ve partnered with award-winning restaurant Hoppers - a Sri Lankan and South Indian restaurant in King’s Cross - to bring you a fan favourite dish, the ‘Banana Leaf Bream’. Boasting a showstopping, spicy fish supper, it guarantees to get taste buds tingling. Hoppers’ Director, Karen Gokani, hosts the cookalong from the Samsung KX Connected Kitchen, where he uses the <a href=\"https://www.samsung.com/uk/refrigerators/family-hub-fridge-freezers/\">Samsung Family Hub Fridge ™</a>, <a href=\"https://www.samsung.com/uk/cooking-appliances/ovens/electric-oven-nv75n5641rs-eu/\">Samsung Dual Flex Oven ™</a> and <a href=\"https://www.samsung.com/uk/apps/smartthings/\">SmartThings app</a> to serve the ultimate connected cooking experience, plus how to take mouth-watering snaps using the new <a href=\"https://www.samsung.com/uk/smartphones/galaxy-s21-5g/buy/?modelCode=SM-G996BZVGEUA&cid=UK_PPC_6388038105_FF~Eval:Brand%2BProd_ProjectU_Tease_KS~BAP_BS~IM_PR~SMART_SB~GS21_OB~SALES_PK~ROAS_FS~LHQ_MD~W_AI~N_MT~EXA_CA~KEW&gclid=Cj0KCQiA0-6ABhDMARIsAFVdQv_3ttr51rnQx-wVOZfkUXxij1yz4iMiQiARbsCRScjihnmG-7qMICgaAurXEALw_wcB&gclsrc=aw.ds\">Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G</a>.",
            "Follow along at 6pm this Valentine's Day (14th February). Here's everything you'll need to join:"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "headline",
          "copy": "Hopper’s Banana Leaf Bream (Serves two)",
          "level": "3"
        },
        {
          "type": "html-list",
          "items": [
            "1 whole sea bream scaled and gutted, or 2 fillets",
            "150g fresh coriander",
            "2 cloves garlic",
            "1-inch ginger",
            "1 green chillies",
            "1 stem fresh lemongrass, (remove the drier, huskier layers and use only the first 2-3 inches of the white bit at the bottom)",
            "3 tbsp fresh grated coconut, or 2 tbsp desiccated coconut soaked for 30 mins ",
            "6-8 curry leaves (ideally fresh)",
            "½ tsp turmeric powder",
            "1 cardamom pod, seeds only",
            "½ tsp fennel seeds",
            "1 tsp cumin seeds",
            "1 tsp tamarind paste",
            "1/3 tsp sugar",
            "1 tbsp coconut oil, or any neutral oil",
            "1/2 lime, juiced",
            "1/2 tsp sea salt",
            "1 lime, to serve",
            "1 large fresh Banana Leaf (you can use baking paper or foil if not!)",
            "Kitchen Foil",
            "A food processor or blender ",
            "Side salad of choice and bottle of Riesling (optional)"
          ]
        }
      ]
